<rss version="2.0"><channel><title>Emilio Eiji - Arduino</title><link>http://blog.emilioeiji.com.br/</link><description>The power of root</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Dec 2014 17:00:00 -0200</lastBuildDate><item><title>Arduino - Controle central telefônica.</title><link>http://blog.emilioeiji.com.br/arduino-controle-central-telefonica.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Controle central telefônica controlando relés via web e com sensor PIR.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;O código está disponível no
&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/emilioeiji/Arduino/blob/master/rele.ino"&gt;github&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As bibliotecas estão disponíveis
&lt;a class="reference external" href="/arquivos/lib_arduino.rar"&gt;aqui.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="cp"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="cpf"&gt;#include &amp;quot;DHT.h&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="cp"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="cp"&gt;#define DHTPIN A0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="cp"&gt;#define DHTTYPE DHT11&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;DHT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;dht&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;DHTPIN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;DHTTYPE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="kt"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;maxtemp&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;mintemp&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="kt"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;maxhum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;minhum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="kt"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;hum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;35&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="kt"&gt;int …&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Emilio</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 12 Dec 2014 17:00:00 -0200</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:blog.emilioeiji.com.br,2014-12-12:/arduino-controle-central-telefonica.html</guid><category>arduino</category><category>relé</category></item><item><title>Arduino - Semáforo interativo</title><link>http://blog.emilioeiji.com.br/arduino-semaforo-interativo.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Daew pessoal!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Testei o projeto do ebook que veio junto com o meu Arduino Uno Rev3,
nele podemos simular um semáforo interativo para pedestres, quando
pressionado o botão o semáforo para carros fecha e abre para os
pedestres.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="http://blog.emilioeiji.com.br/images/semaforo_interativo_projeto.png"&gt;&lt;img alt="image0" src="http://blog.emilioeiji.com.br/images/semaforo_interativo_projeto.png" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
Cricuito para o projeto.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Código:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Projeto Semaforo interativo&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="kt"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;carRed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="kt"&gt;int …&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Emilio</dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 29 Sep 2012 15:49:00 -0300</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:blog.emilioeiji.com.br,2012-09-29:/arduino-semaforo-interativo.html</guid><category>arduino</category><category>semaforo</category><category>led</category></item><item><title>Arduino Uno - Sensor LDR e LM35 apresentando informações no display 16x2</title><link>http://blog.emilioeiji.com.br/arduino-uno-sensor-ldr-e-lm35-apresentando-informacoes-no-display-16x2.html</link><description>&lt;div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="http://blog.emilioeiji.com.br/images/20120923_231707%5B1%5D.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="image0" src="http://blog.emilioeiji.com.br/images/20120923_231707%5B1%5D.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
